<indexterm><primary>GtkFontSelection:preview-text</primary></indexterm><programlisting>  preview-text             <link linkend="gchararray">gchararray</link>            : Read / Write</programlisting>
<para>The text to display in order to demonstrate the selected font.</para><para>Default value: "abcdefghijk ABCDEFGHIJK"</para>
</refsect2>

